 Tanguy Pepiot , a steeplechase runner for the University of Oregon , had a clear lead on his rival Meron Simon , who competes for University of Washington .
But at a track meet in Eugene , Oregon a crowd of more than 3,000 people saw the distance evaporate after Pepiot raised his hands in 100m to go .
Simon 's time , 8:57.86 , exceeded his personal record by 15 seconds .